replyTime":"2021-02-19T14:08:32.000Z","msg":"卡素拿 or 柏圖 只會去依2間, 早排隻貓公都試過<br />\n搞左成個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T14:10:14.000Z","msg":"我諗都有兩個月我搞咗<br />\n睇過兩次醫生兩次都係食完藥好咗少少<br />\n跟住又嚟過又去唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a5e73179f04fee7f5e79f51e7907b2a16df793d","tid":2414581,"uid":389860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fa277d111c363e995aaf1cbc941a45c5ce6d91e","tid":2414581,"uid":250105,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:59:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T14:11:29.000Z","msg":"見佢好似新開 <br />\n如果book唔到嗰兩間就會帶去睇呢間<br />\n都係果句不勝感激<br />\n唔該晒咁多位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係勁擔心為咗呢件事已經同我媽咪嘈左幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望佢可以快啲好返"},{"pid":"534f3f64fb7df714a997251b1f10821eaac41ca4","tid":2414581,"uid":82310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T14:24:05.000Z","msg":"我狗狗早一個星期都係exactly嘔血，係腸胃炎，話食物／環境轉變得太快就會導致咁，我帶咗佢去愛護動物協會，佢哋有夜診，價錢都唔貴，我知愛護動物協會風評唔太好，但我見元朗區啲夜診啲評價仲參差。<br />\n<br />\n至於元朗我諗都係柏圖卡素拿<br />\n聽狗友講卡素拿急症可以打到尖<br />\n柏圖就你死你事（我照狗友原話引述only）<br />\n另外我自己有一次狗狗急事（食咗舊骨）帶咗佢去柏圖<br />\n個護士話冇位叫我哋去對面間診所<br />\n叫做元生動物醫院<br />\n檢查收費開藥都好正常<br />\n不過上網係完全冇人Review的<br />\n<br />\n最後係我嗰搵診所是 come across 一個獸醫資料庫 app<br />\n裡面記錄咗各區獸醫同投訴成立記錄<br />\n不過上次上嚟兒登分享比人當我賣廣告<br />\n我今次四重 hide 加唔貼 link 算了<br />\n<br />\n利申：not affiliate，希望以上資料幫到你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2cc3bdca99c3f1ff13a7e1411979558132f501d","tid":2414581,"uid":82310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"534f3f64fb7df714a997251b1f10821eaac41ca4","tid":2414581,"uid":82310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T14:24:05.000Z","msg":"我狗狗早一個星期都係exactly嘔血，係腸胃炎，話食物／環境轉變得太快就會導致咁，我帶咗佢去愛護動物協會，佢哋有夜診，價錢都唔貴，我知愛護動物協會風評唔太好，但我見元朗區啲夜診啲評價仲參差。<br />\n<br />\n至於元朗我諗都係柏圖卡素拿<br />\n聽狗友講卡素拿急症可以打到尖<br />\n柏圖就你死你事（我照狗友原話引述only）<br />\n另外我自己有一次狗狗急事（食咗舊骨）帶咗佢去柏圖<br />\n個護士話冇位叫我哋去對面間診所<br />\n叫做元生動物醫院<br />\n檢查收費開藥都好正常<br />\n不過上網係完全冇人Review的<br />\n<br />\n最後係我嗰搵診所是 come across 一個獸醫資料庫 app<br />\n裡面記錄咗各區獸醫同投訴成立記錄<br />\n不過上次上嚟兒登分享比人當我賣廣告<br />\n我今次四重 hide 加唔貼 link 算了<br />\n<br />\n利申：not affiliate，希望以上資料幫到你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T14:25:40.000Z","msg":"打錯字，疴血便加嘔，冇嘔血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d9ae8d9c151a9e21e3c17c8ff4a969527f6846e","tid":2414581,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T14:36:10.000Z","msg":"柏圖專一有睇開。推！<br />\n唔介意屯門，樊展霆醫生！"},{"pid":"f1559c22744c11dc08fa1f25a5003fbe922cab87","tid":2414581,"uid":250105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T14:45:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af64df1555253f295dbb697691b356fd6d4370e6","tid"